<!-- Description -->
<div class="row para">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 col-md-offset-2 col-md-offset-2">
<hr width="100px" align="left"/>
<p>Hi, my name is Debashis Barman. I'm a 21 years old college guy who is currently doing Bachelor of Technology in Computer Science and Engineering at <a target="_blank" href="http://dbuniversity.ac.in">Assam Don Bosco University</a> in Guwahati, India. I have been addicted to the Internet since I was young and started making websites since I was in 11. I'm mostly interested in front end web designing but also otherwise enjoy any kind of programming (specially C and Kernel programming) and web development works.</p>
<p>I try to make the websites I design and build as simple and intuitive to use as possible whilst still having a unique aesthetic appeal. I specialise in responsive front-end design, HTML/CSS and web typography.</p>
<p>When I'm free, I spend my time exploring places and beyond, adventuring in the wilderness, learning about the world, working on tiny side projects, writing, romancing my <em>lovely girlfriend</em>, sketching and doodling, <span class="fun">reading</span> short stories and novels, listening to music and playing games. And internet. I love internet.</p>
</div>
</div>

